    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.</p><p>The sword has [[/r 1d8 + 1]] charges. If you score a critical hit against a creature that has fewer than 100 HP, it must succeed on a [[/save 15 CON]] or be slain instantly as the sword tears its life force from its body (a Construct or an Undead is immune). The sword loses 1 charge if the creature is slain. When the sword has no charges remaining, it loses this property.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-SRoLPWSush8hua5K\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p><em>Weapon (Any Sword), Very Rare, 8,800 gp (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>Create the final magic item by selection the appropriate mundane item and dragging an enchantment from the <q>Advancement &amp; Effects</q> tab to that item.</p></section>",
